videoSnippet.title: How Come MY Opponent Never Blunders? | Mamedyarov vs Navara | Batumi Chess Olympiad (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Shakhriyar Mamedyarov vs David Navara
43rd Chess Olympiad (2018), rd 6, Sep-30 
Queen's Gambit Declined: Semi-Tarrasch Defense. Exchange Variation (D41)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 d5 3. c4 e6 4. Nc3 c5 5. cd5 Nd5 6. e4 Nc3 7. bc3 cd4 8. cd4 Bb4 9. Bd2 Bd2 10. Qd2 O-O 11. Bc4 Nd7 12. O-O b6 13. Rad1 Bb7 14. Rfe1 Rc8 15. Bb3 Re8 16. h3 h6 17. Qf4 Qc7 18. e5 Nf8 19. Nd2 Ng6 20. Qg4 b5 21. Ne4 Be4 22. Qe4 a5 23. d5 ed5 24. Rd5 a4 25. Bd1 Qb7 26. Bf3 Ne7 27. Rd6 Qe4 28. Be4 Ng6 29. e6 Nf4 30. ef7 Kf7 31. g3 Ke7 32. Rd2 Ne6 33. Rd5 b4 34. f4 b3 35. ab3 ab3 36. Bg6 Rf8 37. f5 Rf6 38. Re6 Re6 39. fe6 b2 40. Rb5 Kf6 41. Bh7
